---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="法人の方へ"
  description="富士タクシーの法人向けサービス。空港・駅送迎・企業研修・冠婚葬祭・役員送迎にジャンボタクシー7台を完備。JTBタクシーチケット対応。南相馬市・福島県内への対応可。"
>

  <!-- ページヒーロー -->
  <section class="page-hero bg-black">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="パンくずリスト">
        <ol>
          <li><a href="/">ホーム</a></li>
          <li aria-hidden="true">›</li>
          <li aria-current="page">法人の方へ</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <p class="eyebrow reveal">Corporate</p>
      <h1 class="reveal">ビジネスの移動を、<br />もっとスマートに。</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__lead reveal">
        空港送迎から企業研修・冠婚葬祭まで。地域最多7台のジャンボタクシーで、大切な移動をサポートします。
      </p>
      <div class="reveal" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">法人見積もりを依頼する</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 法人向けサービス一覧 -->
  <section class="section bg-black">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
        <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
        <h2 style="color:var(--fuji-white);">法人向け<span style="color:var(--fuji-yellow);">サービス一覧</span></h2>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem auto;"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="corporate-grid reveal">
        <div class="corporate-card">
          <div class="corporate-card__header">
            <span class="corporate-card__num">01</span>
            <span class="corporate-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">✈️</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="corporate-card__title">空港・駅の送迎</h3>
          <p class="corporate-card__text">仙台空港・福島空港・各新幹線駅。事前予約で確実に対応。大切なお客様の到着に万全の体制でお迎えします。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="corporate-card">
          <div class="corporate-card__header">
            <span class="corporate-card__num">02</span>
            <span class="corporate-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">🏢</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="corporate-card__title">企業研修・視察</h3>
          <p class="corporate-card__text">複数名の移動もジャンボタクシー1台で。南相馬市内外の研修・視察をスムーズにサポートします。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="corporate-card">
          <div class="corporate-card__header">
            <span class="corporate-card__num">03</span>
            <span class="corporate-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">💐</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="corporate-card__title">冠婚葬祭送迎</h3>
          <p class="corporate-card__text">大切なご来賓・ゲストの送迎を丁寧に。礼儀正しいドライバーが大切な式に相応しい対応でお迎えします。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="corporate-card">
          <div class="corporate-card__header">
            <span class="corporate-card__num">04</span>
            <span class="corporate-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">🎩</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="corporate-card__title">役員・VIP送迎</h3>
          <p class="corporate-card__text">接客態度に定評あり。大切なお客様の移動に安心してお任せください。信頼とプロ意識で対応します。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ジャンボタクシー特集 -->
  <section class="section bg-yellow">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="jumbo-feature reveal">
        <div class="jumbo-feature__main">
          <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--fuji-black);">Jumbo Taxi</p>
          <h2 style="color: var(--fuji-black);">地域最多 <span style="font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);">7</span> 台保有</h2>
          <p style="color: var(--fuji-black); font-size: var(--text-lg); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">最大9名が1台で移動。大人数でも分乗不要。</p>
          <div class="jumbo-tags">
            <span class="jumbo-tag">冠婚葬祭</span>
            <span class="jumbo-tag">家族旅行</span>
            <span class="jumbo-tag">企業研修</span>
            <span class="jumbo-tag">空港送迎</span>
            <span class="jumbo-tag">駅送迎</span>
            <span class="jumbo-tag">視察</span>
            <span class="jumbo-tag">グループ旅行</span>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--outline-dark">まず見積もりを依頼する</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="jumbo-feature__stats">
          <div class="jumbo-stat">
            <p class="jumbo-stat__num">7</p>
            <p class="jumbo-stat__label">台保有</p>
          </div>
          <div class="jumbo-stat">
            <p class="jumbo-stat__num">9</p>
            <p class="jumbo-stat__label">名乗車可</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 対応決済・チケット -->
  <section class="section bg-black">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
        <p class="eyebrow">Payment</p>
        <h2>対応決済・チケット</h2>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem auto;"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="payment-grid reveal">
        <div class="payment-item">
          <div class="payment-item__icon">🎫</div>
          <h3 class="payment-item__title">タクシーチケット対応</h3>
          <p class="payment-item__text">富士タクシー独自のタクシーチケット・JTBタクシーチケット・愛のタクシーチケット・NO.1タクシーチケットに対応。法人の経費精算をシンプルに。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="payment-item">
          <div class="payment-item__icon">💳</div>
          <h3 class="payment-item__title">クレカ・QR・電子マネー</h3>
          <p class="payment-item__text">VISA / Mastercard / JCB / AMEX / PayPay / AEON Pay / 交通系IC など10種以上対応。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="payment-item">
          <div class="payment-item__icon">📋</div>
          <h3 class="payment-item__title">法人請求書払い</h3>
          <p class="payment-item__text">法人様の請求書払いについては要相談。継続的なご利用についてもお気軽にお問い合わせください。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- メディア取材実績 -->
  <section class="section bg-soft">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
        <p class="eyebrow">Media</p>
        <h2>メディア取材実績</h2>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem auto;"></div>
        <p style="max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--fuji-gray-muted);">
          テレビ局・新聞社などメディアからの取材対応実績を多数有しています。<br />
          取材のご依頼・ご相談はお気軽にお問い合わせください。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="media-badges reveal">
        <div class="media-badge">
          <span class="media-badge__icon">📺</span>
          <span class="media-badge__label">テレビ局</span>
        </div>
        <div class="media-badge">
          <span class="media-badge__icon">📰</span>
          <span class="media-badge__label">新聞社</span>
        </div>
        <div class="media-badge">
          <span class="media-badge__icon">🎙️</span>
          <span class="media-badge__label">取材対応実績多数</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--primary">取材のお問い合わせはこちら</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ご利用の流れ -->
  <section class="section bg-black" aria-labelledby="flow-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--fuji-yellow);">Flow</p>
        <h2 id="flow-heading" style="color: var(--fuji-white);">ご利用の流れ</h2>
        <div class="divider" style="margin: 1rem auto; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);"></div>
        <p style="color: var(--fuji-gray-muted); max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.8;">
          お問い合わせからご乗車まで、わかりやすい3ステップです。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flow-steps reveal">
        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="flow-step__left">
            <div class="flow-step__num">01</div>
            <div class="flow-step__line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step__body">
            <div class="flow-step__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12 19.79 19.79 0 0 1 1.61 3.41 2 2 0 0 1 3.6 1h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.57a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l.95-.95a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="flow-step__title">お電話またはWebでご連絡</h3>
            <p class="flow-step__text">本社（<a href="tel:0244442543" style="color:var(--fuji-yellow);">0244-44-2543</a>）またはWebフォームよりご連絡ください。法人のお問い合わせも歓迎です。まずはお気軽にどうぞ。</p>
            <div class="flow-step__tags">
              <span class="flow-tag">📞 電話</span>
              <span class="flow-tag">🌐 Webフォーム</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="flow-step__left">
            <div class="flow-step__num">02</div>
            <div class="flow-step__line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step__body">
            <div class="flow-step__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="flow-step__title">日時・人数・行先をご確認</h3>
            <p class="flow-step__text">ご希望の日時・人数・乗車場所・目的地をお知らせください。詳細を確認のうえ、担当者より折り返しご連絡いたします。</p>
            <div class="flow-step__tags">
              <span class="flow-tag">📅 日時</span>
              <span class="flow-tag">👥 人数</span>
              <span class="flow-tag">📍 乗降場所</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-step flow-step--last">
          <div class="flow-step__left">
            <div class="flow-step__num flow-step__num--final">03</div>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-step__body">
            <div class="flow-step__icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="flow-step__title">当日、ご指定の場所へお迎え</h3>
            <p class="flow-step__text">ご指定の日時・場所へ確実にお迎えにあがります。現着通知もお伝えできますので、お待たせしません。</p>
            <div class="flow-step__tags">
              <span class="flow-tag flow-tag--yellow">✅ 現着通知あり</span>
              <span class="flow-tag flow-tag--yellow">✅ 時間厳守</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTAバナー -->
  <section class="section bg-yellow">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-banner reveal">
        <h2 class="cta-h2" style="color:var(--fuji-black);">
          まずはお電話でご相談ください
        </h2>
        <p style="color: var(--fuji-black); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: var(--text-lg);">
          法人・大口のご利用も、まずはお気軽に。
        </p>
        <div class="cta-banner__btns">
          <a href="tel:0244442543" class="btn btn--outline-dark">📞 0244-44-2543（本社）</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--outline-dark">Webで見積もりを依頼する</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding-block: 5rem 4rem;
  }
  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--fuji-white);
    margin-block: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .page-hero__lead {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--fuji-gray-muted);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  .breadcrumb ol {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    list-style: none;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--fuji-gray-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--fuji-gray-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--fuji-yellow); }

  /* 法人サービスカード */
  .corporate-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .corporate-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .corporate-card {
    background: var(--fuji-black-card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-left: 4px solid rgba(245,200,0,0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    transition: border-left-color 0.25s ease, background 0.25s ease;
  }
  .corporate-card:hover {
    border-left-color: var(--fuji-yellow);
    background: rgba(245,200,0,0.04);
  }
  .corporate-card__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .corporate-card__num {
    font-family: var(--font-en);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--fuji-yellow);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .corporate-card__icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }
  .corporate-card__title {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--fuji-white);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .corporate-card__text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--fuji-gray-muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  /* ジャンボ特集 */
  .jumbo-feature {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .jumbo-feature { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  .jumbo-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .jumbo-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--fuji-black);
  }
  .jumbo-feature__stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .jumbo-stat {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 120px;
  }
  .jumbo-stat__num {
    font-family: var(--font-en);
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--fuji-black);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .jumbo-stat__label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--fuji-black);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  /* 決済グリッド */
  .payment-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .payment-item {
    background: var(--fuji-black-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .payment-item__icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .payment-item__title {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--fuji-white);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .payment-item__text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--fuji-gray-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ご利用の流れ（タイムライン型） */
  .flow-steps {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .flow-step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr;
    gap: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .flow-step__left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .flow-step__num {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(245,200,0,0.12);
    border: 2px solid var(--fuji-yellow);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-en);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--fuji-yellow);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .flow-step__num--final {
    background: var(--fuji-yellow);
    color: var(--fuji-black);
  }

  .flow-step__line {
    width: 2px;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(245,200,0,0.4), rgba(245,200,0,0.1));
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .flow-step__body {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .flow-step--last .flow-step__body {
    border-color: rgba(245,200,0,0.2);
    background: rgba(245,200,0,0.04);
  }

  .flow-step__icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: rgba(245,200,0,0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--fuji-yellow);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .flow-step__title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--fuji-white);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .flow-step__text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--fuji-gray-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .flow-step__tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .flow-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    color: var(--fuji-gray-muted);
  }

  .flow-tag--yellow {
    background: rgba(245,200,0,0.1);
    border-color: rgba(245,200,0,0.25);
    color: var(--fuji-yellow);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .flow-step { grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 0 1rem; }
    .flow-step__num { width: 44px; height: 44px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  }

  .cta-banner { text-align: center; }
  .cta-banner__btns {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* メディアバッジ */
  .media-badges {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .media-badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    background: var(--fuji-white);
    border: 2px solid var(--fuji-yellow);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .media-badge__icon { font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .media-badge__label { color: var(--fuji-black); }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .reveal.is-visible {
